<title>bạtt dmwʿy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1-(bạtt dmwʿy ʿly̱ ạlkẖdyn mn ạ̉ḥzạny wạ̉nyny
 bṣyt ḥwạlyạ sẖmạl wymyn mlqytsẖ ḥd ywạsyny)2
 (lkn fy lḥẓh ạ̉ftkrt ạ̉nh wḥdk btqdr tḥs byạ )2
 mạhw msẖ gẖrybh ạ̉ṣl ạ̉nạ ạ̉bnh wqlt ạ̹nh ạlḥmwl ʿlyạ
 2-(bbky ʿly̱ ḥạly wmrḍy ạlly ạlạ̉ṭbạʾ fyh ạ̉ḥtạrwạ
 wsnyn ṭwylh wạ̉nạ fy ạ̉lmy zy ạlly yạ mạ ktyr ʿạnwạ)2
 (lkn fy lḥẓh ạ̉ftkrt ạ̉ydk yạ yswʿ dy̱ yạmạ sẖfyt ktyr)2
 dạ ḥty̱ lw ạ̉lms hdb tẖwbk yqf ạlnzyf wyṣyr tḥryr
 3-(msẖ ʿạrf lyh kl ạlạ̉bwạb mqfwlh dạymạaⁿ qdạmy
 ḥty̱ ḥbạyby wạlạ̉ṣḥạb mmkn fy lḥẓh tnsạny)2
 (lkn fy lḥẓh ạ̉ftkrt ạ̉nk bklmh tftḥ wlạ ḥd yqfl)2
 wṣrt ṣạḥby wḥbyb lạ̉nk ʿynk ʿlyạ wlạ mrh tgẖfl
 4-(mạlt sfynty fy ạlmyh wạlmwj mksẖr ạ̉nyạbh
 wạlbḥr hạyj wḥwạlyạ ʿmạl byʿly̱ bạ̉mwạjh )2
 (lkn fy lḥẓh ạ̉ftkrt ạ̉nk ạlbḥr wạlryḥ dạ mn ṣnyʿk)2
 tqdr bklmh yạ yswʿ tqwlhạ ạlmwj wkl ạlryạḥ tṭyʿk</lyrics>
</song>